OL,5, Actor Bernard Hill, best known for     
OL,6, roles in Titanic and Lord of the Rings,
OL,7, has died aged 79.                      
OL,9,FHe played Captain Edward Smith in the  
OL,10,F1997 Oscar-winning film and King       
OL,11,FTheoden in the Lord of the Rings.      
OL,13,FHis breakout role was in 1982 BBC TV   
OL,14,Fdrama Boys from the Blackstuff, where  
OL,15,Fhe portrayed Yosser Hughes, a character
OL,16,Fwho struggled - and often failed - to  
OL,17,Fcope with unemployment in Liverpool.   
OL,19,FHe died early on Sunday morning, his   
OL,20,Fagent Lou Coulson confirmed.           
